      "content": "i mean i get the emissions part, but what about the stuff no one talks about? like the massive amount of mining for minerals needed for wind turbines and batteries? feels like we're just trading one kind of environmental destruction for another. is wind actually \"clean\" if the supply chain is so messy?",
